ss=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Multiset/Defs.html#Multiset\">Multiset</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/SuperSymmetry/SU5/ChargeSpectrum/Basic.html#SuperSymmetry.SU5.ChargeSpectrum\">ChargeSpectrum</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span>)</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Auxiliary recursive function to define `viableChargesMultiset`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/SuperSymmetry/SU5/ChargeSpectrum/PhenoClosed.html#SuperSymmetry.SU5.ChargeSpectrum.viableChargesMultiset.aux","kind":"def","line":400,"name":"SuperSymmetry.SU5.ChargeSpectrum.viableChargesMultiset.aux","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L400-L409"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">unsafe def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/SuperSymmetry/SU5/ChargeSpectrum/PhenoClosed.html#SuperSymmetry.SU5.ChargeSpectrum.viableChargesMultiset\"><span class=\"name\">SuperSymmetry</span>.<span class=\"name\">SU5</span>.<span class=\"name\">ChargeSpectrum</span>.<span class=\"name\">viableChargesMultiset</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#DecidableEq\">DecidableEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommGroup\">AddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">S5 </span><span class=\"fn\">S10</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Finset/Defs.html#Finset\">Finset</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span>